<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a6Aug1934"><font color="red">6 August 1934</font> <i>NLMS</i> (Paul L&eacute;on to Messrs Monro Saw): Mr Joyce has taken a new flat &hellip; still being arranged and on the other hand Mr Joyce is away on a holiday &hellip; Mr Joyce tells me that when he was last in England he left with Thos Cook a somewhat large box with his books and he asks you kindly to have them sent to Paris. </div>
